<br>
the symbol benefits the GROUP and therefore the cost should be that of the group not that of the cleric or tank.  i think the trick is finding a good solution.  i like the comments of some clerics here that they will use their judgement to determine when to share the gems with group members.  you are right, some greedy clerics may abuse that.  so?  if you're looking for perfect solutions you've come to the wrong place.<br>
